about.summary: Performs the 'Baumgartner-Weiss-Schindler' two-sample test of equal probability distributions, <doi:10.2307/2533862>. Also performs similar rank-based tests for equal probability distributions due to Neuhauser <doi:10.1080/10485250108832874> and Murakami <doi:10.1080/00949655.2010.551516>.

name: r-bwstest
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.2.2' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-bwstest
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  fn: BWStest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/BWStest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/BWStest/BWStest_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: faff1dd698f1673a6befacb94d14281077d4c19be035a0a3bf85d77c1dfd5509

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1003
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.3
    - r-memoise
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.3
    - r-memoise

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('BWStest')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('BWStest')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/shabbychef/BWStest
  license: LGPL-3
  summary: Performs the 'Baumgartner-Weiss-Schindler' two-sample test of equal probability distributions,
    <doi:10.2307/2533862>. Also performs similar rank-based tests for equal probability
    distributions due to Neuhauser <doi:10.1080/10485250108832874> and Murakami <doi:10.1080/00949655.2010.551516>.
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/LGPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - johanneskoester
    - bgruening
    - daler
    - jdblischak
    - cbrueffer
    - dbast
    - apcamargo
